καταχθόνιος\">Καταχθονίοις</span>  <span data-text=\"Δαίμοσιν\" data-n=\"15\" data-lemma=\"δαίμων\">Δαίμοσιν</span>  <span data-text=\"χαῖρε\" data-n=\"20\" data-lemma=\"χαίρω\">χαῖρε</span>  <span data-text=\"παροδεῖτα\" data-n=\"25\" data-lemma=\"παροδίτης\">παροδεῖτα</span>  <span data-text=\"χαίρετε\" data-n=\"30\" data-lemma=\"χαίρω\">χαίρετε</span> ΠΟΝΠΕ <span data-text=\"τεκνίον\" data-n=\"40\" data-lemma=\"τεκνίον\">τεκνίον</span>  <span data-text=\"ἐνθάδε\" data-n=\"45\" data-lemma=\"ἐνθάδε\">ἐνθάδε</span>  <span data-text=\"κε͂τε\" data-n=\"50\" data-lemma=\"κεῖμαι\">κε͂τε</span>  <span data-text=\"θανεῖν\" data-n=\"55\" data-lemma=\"θνῄσκω\">θανεῖν</span>  <span data-text=\"πέπροται\" data-n=\"60\" data-lemma=\"πορεῖν\">πέπροται</span>  <span data-text=\"πᾶσιν\" data-n=\"70\" data-lemma=\"πᾶς\">πᾶσιν</span>  </span></div>  <p class=\"miniapp\"></p></div><div class=\"attribution\">Text encoding: Jonathan Prag</div><div id=\"edition-diplomatic\" lang=\"grc\"><div class=\"textpart\" lang=\"grc\"><span class=\"ab\" id=\"div-diplomatic\"><a id=\"al1-diplomatic\"><!--0--></a><span class=\"linenumber\">1</span><span data-text=\"Θεοῖς\" data-n=\"5\" data-lemma=\"θεός\">Θ</span><span data-text=\"Καταχθονίοις\" data-n=\"10\" data-lemma=\"καταχθόνιος\">Κ</span><span data-text=\"Δαίμοσιν\" data-n=\"15\" data-lemma=\"δαίμων\">Δ</span><br id=\"al2-diplomatic\"><span class=\"linenumber\">2</span><span data-text=\"χαῖρε\" data-n=\"20\" data-lemma=\"χαίρω\">ΧΑΙΡΕ</span><span data-text=\"παροδεῖτα\" data-n=\"25\" data-lemma=\"παροδίτης\">ΠΑΡΟΔΕΙΤΑ</span><br id=\"al3-diplomatic\"><span class=\"linenumber\">3</span><span data-text=\"χαίρετε\" data-n=\"30\" data-lemma=\"χαίρω\">ΧΑΙΡΕΤΕ</span>ΠΟΝΠΕ<span data-text=\"τεκνίον\" data-n=\"40\" data-lemma=\"τεκνίον\">ΤΕΚΝΙΟΝ</span><br id=\"al4-diplomatic\"><span class=\"linenumber\">4</span><span data-text=\"ἐνθάδε\" data-n=\"45\" data-lemma=\"ἐνθάδε\">ΕΝΘΑΔΕ</span><span data-text=\"κε͂τε\" data-n=\"50\" data-lemma=\"κεῖμαι\">ΚΕΤΕ</span><br id=\"al5-diplomatic\"><span class=\"linenumber\">5</span><span data-text=\"θανεῖν\" data-n=\"55\" data-lemma=\"θνῄσκω\">ΘΑΝΕΙΝ</span><span data-text=\"πέπροταιπέπρωται\" data-n=\"60\" data-lemma=\"πορεῖν\">ΠΕΠΡΟΤΑΙ</span><br id=\"al6-diplomatic\"><span class=\"linenumber\">6</span><span data-text=\"πᾶσιν\" data-n=\"70\" data-lemma=\"πᾶς\">ΠΑΣΙΝ</span></span></div><p class=\"miniapp\">l.5 reg., orig. ΠΕΠΡΟΤΑΙπέπροται</p></div><div class=\"attribution\">Text encoding: Dmitry Dundua, Robert Crellin</div><div id=\"edition-diplomatic-simple-lemmatized\"><div class=\"textpart\"><span class=\"ab\" id=\"div-diplomatic\"><span data-text=\"Θεοῖς\" data-n=\"5\" data-lemma=\"θεός\">ΘΕΟΙΣ</span><span data-text=\"Καταχθονίοις\" data-n=\"10\" data-lemma=\"καταχθόνιος\">ΚΑΤΑΧΘΟΝΙΟΙΣ</span><span data-text=\"Δαίμοσιν\" data-n=\"15\" data-lemma=\"δαίμων\">ΔΑΙΜΟΣΙΝ</span><span data-text=\"χαῖρε\" data-n=\"20\" data-lemma=\"χαίρω\">ΧΑΙΡΕ</span><span data-text=\"παροδεῖτα\" data-n=\"25\" data-lemma=\"παροδίτης\">ΠΑΡΟΔΕΙΤΑ</span><span data-text=\"χαίρετε\" data-n=\"30\" data-lemma=\"χαίρω\">ΧΑΙΡΕΤΕ</span>ΠΟΝΠΕ<span data-text=\"τεκνίον\" data-n=\"40\" data-lemma=\"τεκνίον\">ΤΕΚΝΙΟΝ</span><span data-text=\"ἐνθάδε\" data-n=\"45\" data-lemma=\"ἐνθάδε\">ΕΝΘΑΔΕ</span><span data-text=\"κε͂τε\" data-n=\"50\" data-lemma=\"κεῖμαι\">ΚΕΤΕ</span><span data-text=\"θανεῖν\" data-n=\"55\" data-lemma=\"θνῄσκω\">ΘΑΝΕΙΝ</span><span data-text=\"πέπροται\" data-n=\"60\" data-lemma=\"πορεῖν\">ΠΕΠΡΟΤΑΙ</span><span data-text=\"πᾶσιν\" data-n=\"70\" data-lemma=\"πᾶς\">ΠΑΣΙΝ</span></span></div><p class=\"miniapp\"></p></div></div>  <div id=\"facsimile-images\"><h2>Facsimile Images</h2><a href=\"ISic003560_tiled.tif\"><img title=\"I.Sicily with the permission of the Assessorato Regionale dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana - Dipartimento dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana\" src=\"ISic003560_tiled-thumb.tif\"></a><a href=\"ISic003560.jpg\"><img title=\"I.Sicily with the permission of the Assessorato Regionale dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana - Dipartimento dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana\" src=\"ISic003560-thumb.jpg\"></a></div>  <div id=\"apparatus\"><h4>Apparatus criticus</h4><ul><li><span>  <span>Text based on comparison of Kaibel, Filippi and SEG, prioritising Kaibel's transcription of the manuscript tradition.</span>  </span>; </li><li><span class=\"3\">3: <span>Kaibel notes that the likely source texts all read ΓΟΝΓΕ</span>  </span></li></ul></div>  <div id=\"translation\"><h2> translation</h2><p class=\"translation-author\">  </p><p>  </p></div>  <div id=\"commentary\"><h2>commentary</h2>  <p>As Korhonen lucidly details, the inscription is one of a series of late 18th century local antiquarian forgeries, constructed on the basis of existing texts, principally those to be found in the 1769 first edition of the corpus of Torremuzza. Kaibel classed the entire series already as forgeries in IG XIV.</p>  </div>  <div id=\"bibliography\"><h2>bibliography</h2>  <ul><li> 52.0905 <a href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000796\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000796</a>  </li><li> Kaibel 1890 <a href=\"https://clio.columbia.edu/catalog/6873760\" target=\"_blank\">29*</a>  <a href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001072\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001072</a>  </li><li> Filippi 2002 75 no. 14/6 <a href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001991\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001991</a>  </li><li> Filippi 2005 69 no.14/6 <a href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10002296\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10002296</a>  </li><li> Korhonen 2017 199 <a href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001484\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001484</a>  </li></ul>  <ul><li></li></ul>  </div>  <div id=\"handnote\"> Line 1    Interlineation line 1 to 2    </div><div id=\"license\"> Licensed under a Creative Commons-Attribution 4.0 licence. </div>",
